# Water Count App 📱💧

A React Native mobile application designed to help users track their daily water intake and stay hydrated. Water Count makes it easy to monitor and maintain healthy hydration habits throughout the day.

## Features

- Track daily water consumption in real-time
- Set personalized daily water intake goals
- Receive friendly reminders to drink water
- View hydration history and patterns
- Simple and intuitive user interface
- Progress visualization with charts
- Customizable measurement units (ml, oz)

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Siddhuu-7/water-count.git
cd water-count
```

2. Install dependencies:
```bash
npm install
```

3. Start the development server:
```bash
npm start
```

4. Run the application:
```bash
npx react-native run-android
# or
npx react-native run-ios
```

## Technologies Used

- React Native
- JavaScript/TypeScript
- AsyncStorage for local data persistence
- React Navigation for routing
- React Native SVG for charts and graphics

